  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个FastAPI应用的架构图，核心是一个Etcd集群做服务发现，还有Worker节点处理请求。我想把它们放在一个叫FastAPI Application的子图里。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FastAPI Application",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，Etcd集群和Worker节点放在同一个子图里。那流量入口怎么处理？需要LoadBalancer吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，需要两个LoadBalancer。一个是入口层的S，另一个是Worker节点C下游的PM。另外还要一个IngressController做七层路由。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把S、A和PM加进去。入口S连到IngressController A，然后A再分发到Worker节点对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "不完全对，Etcd集群P和第一个Worker PR也要连到A。而且P、PR、S这三个绿色组件都要连到另一个Worker节点C，不是只连A。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "明白了，我重新画一下：P、PR、S都指向A，同时P、PR、S也指向C。然后C再连到PM和RedisCache AU。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，但PM也要连到AU，这个缓存依赖别漏了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已加上PM到AU的连接。现在来设置样式，Etcd和Worker节点用绿色，Ingress和第二个LoadBalancer用蓝色，Redis用橙色，stroke-width都2px可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "style",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "绿色用#82b366，蓝色用#6c8ebf，橙色用#d79b00。填充色分别是#d5e8d4、#dae8fc、#ffe6cc。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "style",
        "stroke",
        "fill"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "样式已应用。确认一下组件命名：P是Infra_EtcdCluster，PR是Infra_WorkerNode，S是Infra_LoadBalancer，A是Infra_IngressController，C是另一个Infra_WorkerNode，PM是第二个Infra_LoadBalancer，AU是Infra_RedisCache。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "命名没问题。不过C和PR都是WorkerNode，只是角色不同，C是处理下游流量的那个。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我注意到P、PR、S到C的连接是实线，但代码里显示的是\"--\"，这是表示无箭头连接还是简写？需要明确方向吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "\"--\"就是无向边，这几个组件之间是双向通信或者松耦合关系，不需要箭头。但C到PM、C到AU、PM到AU是有明确方向的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整，无向边保持\"--\"，有向边我会用\"--\"表示。现在整个子图结构都封装在FastAPI Application里了，所有7个节点和样式都设置完成。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FastAPI Application",
        "subgraph",
        "style"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "最后检查一下，Etcd集群P和Worker PR、LoadBalancer S这三个基础设施组件，既要连到IngressController做入口，又要直连Worker C做内部通信，这个逻辑要清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认无误。架构图已完成：三层结构清晰，绿色基础设施层、蓝色网关层、橙色缓存层，所有连接关系符合你的描述。",
